com.bigdata.rawstore

Interface IWORM

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBufferStrategy, AbstractRawWormStore, BasicBufferStrategy, DirectBufferStrategy, DiskBackedBufferStrategy, DiskOnlyStrategy, MappedBufferStrategy, SimpleFileRawStore, SimpleMemoryRawStore, TemporaryRawStore, TemporaryStore, TransientBufferStrategy, WORMStrategy

    public interface IWORM
    A marker interface for a store that supports Write Once Read Many (eg, an append only store vs a store where storage may be reused as records are logically deleted).
